data.description: Your chance to live in the highly desirable neighborhood of Glen Laurel is here! This spacious 4/2 sits on 1.25 acres with pond access. Natural light in every room of this beautiful home makes it bright and open. The large kitchen has an eat in breakfast nook and plenty of cabinets along with an island, the split floor plan is perfect for a family, separate dining room and office/bonus room. Tile in the kitchen and the living room, master bedroom has LVP. Relax with a good soak in the master jacuzzi tub. The backyard is fully fenced and is truly one of a kind with a screened in patio and open patio along with a very cute work shed with storage. Bring your boat or RV as this property has a oversized toy shelter with water/electricity already hooked up! Schedule your showing today!
